text: Jordanoleiopus fenestrella is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Karl Jordan in 1903.BioLib.cz - Jordanoleiopus. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Jordanoleiopus Category:Beetles described in 1903 Category:Taxa named by Karl Jordan
